Package oracle.express.spl

Contains classes that support the execution of OLAP DML commands in Oracle OLAP.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SPLExecutor
    An object that accepts a String and sends it to Oracle OLAP for internal execution or evaluation.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    NAValueException
    Indicates that the return value is NA for the DML expression that you attempted to evaluate using an SPLExecutor.

Package oracle.express.spl Description
